text:
Bende boii
         First-year we used to play cards and games lot. It was a nice year
       Yaar apni kabhi saath inter it nahi hui
  Best wishes to you too
author: Nikhil  Sharma

text:
Kya re bhadwe bhul hi gaye ho lagta hai
bade busy chalre ho night duty jo lagi hui hai
Bhai 2nd year was lit raat bhar bhencho fifa khelte the subah naasta karke so jate the. 
Solanki ke ghuste hi tere pe ek long range padta tha .  Subah utha ke camp jana bhencho apne dono ki hi mout aati thi usme. Bhai woh raat ko fifa khelte khelte jo discussions hote the should go with us to the grave.
Overall u were a fun guy to be roomies with.  
Bhadwe aao kabhi jaipur solanki ko leke. 
Aur bc kabhi to yaad karlia kar.
Chal ja gand mara
author: Nikhil  Sharma

text:
Bhai jab tu aaya tha tereko ek bhi normal khane ka naam nahi pata tha ab saala bohut aage nikal gaye ho be tum.  Saale abhi tak tu Ladakh nahi ghoomaya na Kitni baar bola hai tujhe . Bhai yaade to bohut banayi hai saath mai 4 saal . 2nd year  summer was nice . Aur gandu mujhe pata hai kyu Delhi ki hi job dhoondi hai tune Bhaiyo ko bhul gaya saale hum sab banglore mai honge. Nice keep doing ur future planning. 
Chalo  Khuda Hafiz
Aur jaldi ek aur trip plan karo be
author: Nikhil  Sharma

text:
From Ur NAAMBAAP(BTW aachus was also a nice name by naveen )
Kya be saale tera naam hi bhul jaata hu. Abhi bhi search bar mai poota daala fir no result found aaya to chok gaya. Fifa to chod de bhai challenge hai aagle saal bhar bhi tu practice karle fir bhi muh kaala hi karwa ke jaega.  Aur bsdk aaj nahi aaj nahi karke bhi har din chalu hote hi tapak jate the.  The more the merrier. Aur gandu saala saare grapes kha jata tha baithe baithe. Saale kabhi dryclean nahi karwaya phir tu woh jacket.  aur jo harkate tumhe gajab kari thi, samuhik shok mana raha tha trip pe.
Aur bc shadi kab hai . Barot madarchod ne apne pillow bohut churaye hai.
It was a nice 4 years with u and also hope there are many more years to come.

ab yeh pad ke bhi rone mat lagna
author: Nikhil  Sharma

text:
Bsdk trip mai bhi saale wohi hostel wale kapde pahen ke hoom raha tha. Bazooka nights were goood.
Aur bsdk poora hi badal gya tu gandu ghar pe rahke. With some Big boy problems now. Aur gandu jab knowledge na ho to pheka mat kar.  yaad hai sale tu atm ne bhi tera kaata tha how much more low can go :) (500 rupay kam laaya tha yeh) 
Maje bhi waise kaafi karay tune 4 saal 
Chal bye, Aur kanpur kab jana ??
author: Nikhil  Sharma

author: Nikhil  Sharma

text:
Aur solanki mia 
Abhi to tujhe aur bohut games harne hai fifa ke mujhse. Jaipur aaja jaldi mast dinbhar khellenge. 5 bot mai maje to the raat bhar Fifa subah breakfast (best was poha sunday)karo fir bas so jao. Best cheez thi jab bhi tu room mai ghoosta tha soni pe hamesha ek long range padta tha. Aur tera woh dance step jo din bhar karta tha tu 
Chalo msg kardio fifa ke liye on sat suns, FYI naambaap hu tera
